(
  'Maximizing ROI: A Data-Driven Approach to Creator Campaigns',
  'maximizing-roi-data-driven-creator-campaigns',
  '<h2>Understanding Campaign Performance</h2><p>Return on investment (ROI) in creator campaigns isn''t just about sales numbers. It''s about understanding the full customer journey and how influencer touchpoints contribute to overall brand success.</p><h3>Key Metrics to Track</h3><ul><li>Engagement rate vs. reach</li><li>Click-through rates and conversions</li><li>Brand sentiment analysis</li><li>Long-term customer value</li></ul><h3>Setting Up for Success</h3><p>The most successful campaigns start with clear objectives and KPIs. Whether you''re focused on brand awareness, lead generation, or direct sales, having the right measurement framework is essential.</p><p>Advanced analytics platforms now provide real-time insights that allow for campaign optimization during execution, not just post-mortem analysis.</p>',
  'Learn how to maximize your creator campaign ROI through strategic data analysis and performance optimization techniques.',
  'published',
  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - INTERVAL ''5 days'',
  '18f1db0f-e358-4415-8b33-c926b03a6904',
