  'Maximize Creator Campaign ROI with Data-Driven Strategies | Beyond Views',
  'Master data-driven approaches to optimize creator campaigns and maximize return on investment with proven analytics strategies.'
),
(
  'Platform Deep Dive: Optimizing Content for TikTok vs Instagram vs YouTube',
  'platform-optimization-tiktok-instagram-youtube',
  '<h2>Understanding Platform Dynamics</h2><p>Each social platform has its unique algorithm, audience behavior, and content preferences. Successful creator partnerships require platform-specific strategies that align with both the creator''s strengths and the platform''s best practices.</p><h3>TikTok: The Algorithm Advantage</h3><p>TikTok''s algorithm favors engagement velocity and completion rates. Content that hooks viewers in the first 3 seconds and maintains attention throughout performs exceptionally well.</p><h3>Instagram: Visual Storytelling</h3><p>Instagram remains the king of visual content. High-quality imagery, consistent aesthetic, and strategic use of Stories and Reels drive engagement and brand discovery.</p><h3>YouTube: Long-form Value</h3><p>YouTube''s algorithm rewards watch time and viewer retention. Educational content, tutorials, and in-depth reviews perform well when creators can maintain audience attention.</p>',
  'Master platform-specific strategies for TikTok, Instagram, and YouTube to optimize your creator content performance.',
  'published',
