  '18f1db0f-e358-4415-8b33-c926b03a6904',
  'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611162617474-5b21e879e113?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80',
  'Platform Optimization Guide: TikTok vs Instagram vs YouTube | Beyond Views',
  'Learn platform-specific optimization strategies for TikTok, Instagram, and YouTube to maximize creator content performance.'
),
(
  'Building Long-Term Creator Partnerships That Drive Results',
  'building-long-term-creator-partnerships',
  '<h2>Beyond One-Off Campaigns</h2><p>The most successful brands are moving away from transactional creator relationships toward long-term partnerships that build authentic brand advocacy and sustained growth.</p><h3>The Partnership Mindset</h3><p>Treating creators as true partners rather than just marketing channels leads to more authentic content, better audience reception, and improved campaign performance over time.</p><h3>Nurturing Creator Relationships</h3><ul><li>Regular communication and feedback</li><li>Creative freedom within brand guidelines</li><li>Fair compensation and growth opportunities</li><li>Mutual support and promotion</li></ul><p>Long-term partnerships allow creators to develop a genuine connection with your brand, resulting in more natural product integrations and higher audience trust.</p>',
  'Discover how to build lasting creator partnerships that go beyond single campaigns to drive sustained brand growth.',
  'published',
  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - INTERVAL ''10 days'',
  '18f1db0f-e358-4415-8b33-c926b03a6904',
  'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600880292203-757bb62b4baf?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80',
  'Building Long-Term Creator Partnerships for Brand Growth | Beyond Views',
  'Learn strategies for developing lasting creator partnerships that drive sustained brand growth and authentic audience engagement.'
),
(
  'The Analytics Revolution: Beyond Vanity Metrics in Influencer Marketing',
  'analytics-revolution-beyond-vanity-metrics',
  '<h2>The Problem with Vanity Metrics</h2><p>For too long, the influencer marketing industry has been obsessed with follower counts and likes. While these metrics aren''t worthless, they don''t tell the complete story of campaign effectiveness or audience quality.</p><h3>Metrics That Matter</h3><p>Modern analytics platforms provide insights into audience authenticity, engagement quality, and conversion potential. Understanding these deeper metrics is crucial for campaign success.</p><h3>Quality Over Quantity</h3><p>A creator with 10K highly engaged, relevant followers often outperforms one with 100K passive followers. The key is understanding audience alignment with your brand values and target demographics.</p><h3>Real-Time Optimization</h3><p>Advanced analytics enable real-time campaign adjustments, allowing brands to optimize content, timing, and messaging based on immediate performance data.</p>',
  'Move beyond vanity metrics and discover the analytics that truly matter for influencer marketing success.',
  'published',
  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - INTERVAL ''2 weeks'',
  '18f1db0f-e358-4415-8b33-c926b03a6904',
  'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80',
  'Beyond Vanity Metrics: Analytics That Drive Results | Beyond Views',
  'Discover meaningful analytics and metrics that go beyond follower counts to drive real influencer marketing success.'
),
(
  'Micro vs Macro: Choosing the Right Influencer Tier for Your Brand',
  'micro-vs-macro-influencer-tier-strategy',
  '<h2>The Influencer Spectrum</h2><p>Understanding the different influencer tiers and their unique advantages is crucial for developing effective campaign strategies. Each tier offers distinct benefits depending on your campaign objectives.</p><h3>Nano-Influencers (1K-10K followers)</h3><ul><li>Highest engagement rates</li><li>Most authentic connections</li><li>Cost-effective for local campaigns</li><li>Strong community trust</li></ul><h3>Micro-Influencers (10K-100K followers)</h3><ul><li>Balanced reach and engagement</li><li>Niche expertise and authority</li><li>Higher conversion rates</li><li>More professional content creation</li></ul><h3>Macro-Influencers (100K-1M followers)</h3><ul><li>Significant reach and awareness</li><li>Professional content quality</li><li>Cross-platform presence</li><li>Established brand partnerships</li></ul><p>The key is aligning influencer tier with campaign goals, budget, and target audience characteristics.</p>',
  'Learn how to choose between micro and macro influencers to optimize your campaign strategy and budget allocation.',
  'draft',
  NULL,
  '18f1db0f-e358-4415-8b33-c926b03a6904',
